<Defs>

  <ThingDef ParentName="LeatherBase">
    <defName>DND_Leather_Owlbear</defName>
    <label>owlbear Featherfur</label>
    <description>This unusual pelt consists of a thick layer of fur covered by an outer layer of feathers. It provides excellent protection, and the sound-muffling feathers provide a hunting stealth bonus to coats (outer-layer torso clothing) made from this material.</description>
    <graphicData>
      <color>(150, 122, 161)</color>
    </graphicData>
    <statBases>
      <MarketValue>4.5</MarketValue>
      <StuffPower_Armor_Sharp>1.24</StuffPower_Armor_Sharp>
      <StuffPower_Armor_Blunt>0.3</StuffPower_Armor_Blunt>
      <StuffPower_Insulation_Cold>24</StuffPower_Insulation_Cold>
      <StuffPower_Insulation_Heat>20</StuffPower_Insulation_Heat>
    </statBases>
    <stuffProps>
      <color>(154,37,161)</color>
      <commonality>0.025</commonality>
      <statFactors>
        <MaxHitPoints>1.5</MaxHitPoints>
        <Beauty>2</Beauty>
      </statFactors>
    </stuffProps>
  </ThingDef>

  <ThingDef ParentName="LeatherBase">
    <defName>DND_Leather_DisplacerBeast</defName>
    <label>Displacer Beast Fur</label>
    <description>A beautiful pelt harvested from a displacer beast. Like a living displacer beast, the pelt occasionally bends light, making it appear a few feet away from its real location. This makes the leather exceptionally difficult to work with, but also confers the same benefit to the wearer if clothing is made from it. The clothing must be fairly large to provide this effect, so it must cover the wearer's torso on the outer layer.</description>
    <graphicData>
      <color>(20,20,20)</color>
    </graphicData>
    <statBases>
      <MarketValue>5.5</MarketValue>
      <StuffPower_Armor_Sharp>1.24</StuffPower_Armor_Sharp>
      <StuffPower_Insulation_Cold>5</StuffPower_Insulation_Cold>
      <StuffPower_Insulation_Heat>26</StuffPower_Insulation_Heat>
      <WorkToMake>3</WorkToMake>
      <WorkToBuild>3</WorkToBuild>
    </statBases>
    <stuffProps>
      <color>(20,20,20)</color>
      <commonality>0.025</commonality>
      <statFactors>
        <MaxHitPoints>1.5</MaxHitPoints>
        <Beauty>3</Beauty>
      </statFactors>
    </stuffProps>
  </ThingDef>
  

